videos.headline: Antoine Davis drops 38, moves within 25 points of NCAA scoring record
videos.description: Detroit Mercy's Antoine Davis scores 38 in a win vs. Purdue Fort Wayne and now trails Pete Maravich's career scoring mark by just 25 points.
